title: Readout of the President's Calls Tonight | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
November 03, 2010

 



Readout of the President's Calls Tonight





	The President tonight called and talked to Reps. Pelosi, Boehner and Hoyer, and Senator McConnell

	In his calls with Rep. Boehner and Sen. McConnell, the President said he was “looking forward to working with him and the Republicans to find common ground, move the country forward and get things done for the American people.”

	A photograph of the President talking with Rep. Boehner is available HERE.
